'''埃里克·弗雷德里克·特朗普'''（{{lang-en|Eric Frederick Trump}}，{{bd|1984年|1月6日}}）是一位美国商人、電視名人和慈善家。 他是[[唐納·川普|唐納·川普]]和[[伊凡娜·川普|伊凡娜·川普]]的次子。他和[[唐納·川普|唐納·川普]]長子，其兄長[[小唐納德·特朗普|小唐纳德]]是[[特朗普集團|特朗普集團]]的受託人，共同执掌集团在全球范围内的收购与开发项目。2006年，他成立了旨在为聖裘德兒童研究醫院筹款的埃里克·特朗普基金。<ref name="ETFWelcome">{{Cite web|url=http://www.erictrumpfoundation.com|title=Welcome|accessdate=2013-06-30|publisher=Eric Trump Foundation|archive-date=2018-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180930221103/http://www.erictrumpfoundation.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 他还是特朗普酒庄的拥有人。<ref>Johnson, Richard. </ref><ref>[http://www.businessinsider.com/meet-donald-trumps-five-children-2015-7 Meet Donald Trump's five children] {{Wayback|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/meet-donald-trumps-five-children-2015-7 |date=20170708014834 }}.</ref>

== 早期的生活和教育 ==
埃里克·特朗普出生于[[曼哈頓|曼哈頓]]，并就读于[[三一學院_(紐約市)|三一學院]]。 他的父母于1992年离婚，当时他只有8岁。2002年他毕业于[[希尔中学|希尔中学]]并随后担任其理事直至2013年。<ref name="celebrityprepschools.com">{{Cite web|url=http://www.celebrityprepschools.com/part5.htm|title=Celebrity Prep Schools|accessdate=2006-11-23|archive-date=2010-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100704060832/http://www.celebrityprepschools.com/part5.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref> 埃里克于2006年加入[[特朗普集團|特朗普集團]]，在此之前他曾就读于[[华盛顿哥伦比亚特区|华盛顿哥伦比亚特区]]的[[乔治城大学|乔治城大学]]并以优异的成绩荣获[[金融|财务]]和[[管理学|管理]]学位。<ref name="cbsnews.com">{{Cite news|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/stories/2003/06/09/48hours/main557757.shtml|title=Eric Trump, American Royalty|date=2003-06-09|publisher=CBS News|accessdate=2006-11-23|archive-date=2007-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070111075719/http://www.cbsnews.com/stories/2003/06/09/48hours/main557757.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 职业和慈善事业 ==

=== 特朗普集团 ===
埃里克是特朗普集团发展和收购方面的执行副总裁。他也在[[全国广播公司|美国全国广播公司]]的[[飛黃騰達|飛黃騰達]]节目中担任是任务顾问和董事会裁判。他的公司责任确保集团在国内外扩张中获得房地产收益。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.dailyfinance.com/2011/06/17/fathers-day-donald-trumps-legacy-kids-who-aim-to-think-big/|title=Donald Trump's Legacy: Kids Who Aim to Think Big|last=Kawamoto|first=Dawn|date=2011-06-17|work=Daily Finance|accessdate=2011-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110620163540/http://www.dailyfinance.com/2011/06/17/fathers-day-donald-trumps-legacy-kids-who-aim-to-think-big/|archive-date=2011-06-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 埃里克与其父长期监督着特朗普高尔夫球场投资组合的扩张，其数量已从他2006年进入集团时的三家达到目前的十五家；其业务遍及[[纽约州|纽约]]、[[新泽西州|新泽西]]、[[宾夕法尼亚州|宾夕法尼亚]]、[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达]]、[[北卡罗来纳州|北卡罗来纳]]、[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚]]和[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]。他在国内外扩张中着重识别和追求不良的高尔夫球物业，并与其姊伊万卡共同负责重新设计并改造位于迈阿密的特朗多拉国家酒店。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.nbcmiami.com/news/Trump-National-Doral-Construction-Ahead-of-Schedule-Eric-Trump-226377351.html|title=Trump National Doral Miami Construction Ahead of Schedule|last=Leon|first=Alexandra|date=2013-10-03|work=NBC 6 South Florida|accessdate=2013-10-03|archive-date=2013-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131003232318/http://www.nbcmiami.com/news/Trump-National-Doral-Construction-Ahead-of-Schedule-Eric-Trump-226377351.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>他和他的兄弟姐妹均参与建立和管理特朗普酒店的收藏物业。埃里克当前管理的全球酒店投资组合包括拉斯维加斯、[[芝加哥|芝加哥]]、[[纽约|纽约]]、[[多伦多|多伦多]]、[[巴拿马|巴拿马]]、[[威基基|威基基]]、[[埃斯特角城|埃斯特角城]]、[[华盛顿哥伦比亚特区|华盛顿哥伦比亚特区]]、[[溫哥華|溫哥華]]、[[菲律宾|菲律宾]]和[[里约热内卢|里约热内卢]]。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.vegasinc.com/business/tourism/2013/apr/02/hired-or-fired-how-trump-doing-after-5-years/|title=Hired or Fired?  How Trump is doing after Five Years in Las Vegas|last=Sylvester|first=Ron|date=2013-04-02|work=VegasInc.com|accessdate=2013-04-02|archive-date=2016-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161101024106/http://vegasinc.com/business/tourism/2013/apr/02/hired-or-fired-how-trump-doing-after-5-years/|dead-url=no}}</ref>他还在[[夏律第鎮|弗吉尼亚州夏洛茨维尔获得克鲁格酒庄园和葡萄园]]，并建立特朗普酒庄。在2013年，王牌赢得了<span>Wine Enthusiast Magazine的</span>"年度明日之星"奖。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.winemag.com/Web-2013/2013-Rising-Star-of-the-Year-Eric-Trump/|title=2013 Rising Star of the Year: Eric Trump|last=Hoover|first=Andrew|date=2013-11-17|work=Wine Enthusiast Magazine|accessdate=2013-11-17|archive-date=2013-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131116155719/http://www.winemag.com/Web-2013/2013-Rising-Star-of-the-Year-Eric-Trump/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2012年，埃里克·特朗普被[[福布斯|福布斯]]杂志评为“30位30岁以下”的顶级[[不動產|地产大亨]]，并被纽约观察家杂志评为“20位重量级青年慈善家”之一。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://observer.com/2013/04/new-yorks-young-philanthropist-powerhouse-eric-trump/|title=New York's Young Philanthropist Powerhouse Eric Trump|last=Davis|first=Peter|date=2013-04-10|work=New York Observer|accessdate=2013-04-10|archive-date=2013-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130412020841/http://observer.com/2013/04/new-yorks-young-philanthropist-powerhouse-eric-trump/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 纽约观察家则是由他的姐夫[[Jared_Kushner|杰瑞德·库什纳]]创办的。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://observer.com/about/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-08-07 |archive-date=2015-11-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151123042444/http://observer.com/about/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 埃里克·特朗普基金会 ===
埃里克·特朗普基金会（ETF）成立于2006年，<ref name="ETFWelcome">{{Cite web|url=http://www.erictrumpfoundation.com|title=Welcome|accessdate=2013-06-30|publisher=Eric Trump Foundation}}</ref>旨在专门为圣裘德儿童研究医院的临终患儿筹集资金。该基金会是一个免税的慈善组织。

== 争议 ==
2010年，[[善待动物组织|善待动物组织]]强烈抨击了埃里克·特朗普与其兄小唐纳德拍摄的White hunter#Hunting in Africa之旅。有照片显示该兄弟在[[辛巴威|津巴布韦]]参加了一个有组织的[[狩獵旅行|狩獵旅行]]并在途中猎杀动物。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/03/13/donald-trump-sons-safari-killing_n_1341596.html|title=Donald Trump's Sons Defend Safari Killing Spree In Zimbabwe (PHOTOS)|last=Kelly|first=Tara|date=2012-03-13|work=The Huffington Post|accessdate=2013-06-30|archive-date=2013-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130519202004/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/03/13/donald-trump-sons-safari-killing_n_1341596.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> [[辛巴威|津巴布韦]]公园和野生生物管理局总干事V. Chandenga发表了一个官方声明支持特朗普兄弟并声称任何违法指控都是“毫无根据”和“虚假的”。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.nypost.com/p/news/business/letter_trump_safari_not_canned_En8UfWq9aDBqVMm8smyqgM|title=Letter: Trump safari not ‘canned’|last=Weiss|first=Lois|date=2012-03-28|work=New York Post|accessdate=2013-06-30|archive-date=2012-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120622023505/http://www.nypost.com/p/news/business/letter_trump_safari_not_canned_En8UfWq9aDBqVMm8smyqgM|dead-url=no}}</ref> 两兄弟通过[[Twitter|Twitter]]申明他们的行为作为猎人和长期户外运动者是合法的。<ref name="yahoo1">{{Cite web|url=http://news.yahoo.com/blogs/sideshow/donald-trump-sons-criticized-brutal-hunting-photos-released-213958504.html|title=Donald Trump's sons criticized after brutal hunting photos released|accessdate=2012-05-07|date=2011-11-15|last=Pfeiffer|first=Eric|work=The Sideshow|publisher=Yahoo! News|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112005019/http://news.yahoo.com/blogs/sideshow/donald-trump-sons-criticized-brutal-hunting-photos-released-213958504.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> [[唐納德·川普|他们的父亲]]也对此发表评论称其完全支持他的儿子们。<ref name="yahoo1">{{Cite web|url=http://news.yahoo.com/blogs/sideshow/donald-trump-sons-criticized-brutal-hunting-photos-released-213958504.html|title=Donald Trump's sons criticized after brutal hunting photos released|accessdate=2012-05-07|date=2011-11-15|last=Pfeiffer|first=Eric|work=The Sideshow|publisher=Yahoo! News}}</ref>2016年8月2日，埃里克·特朗普出现在CBS今晨节目上并被要求评论他其父在前一日今日美國节目中有关女儿曾在工作场所遭到性骚扰并希望她会找到另一家公司工作或开关的职业生涯的争议性言论。埃里克说"伊万卡是一个强有力的女人，她不会允许自己轻易放弃。”埃里克的评论收到了来自个人和组织的广泛批评，批评者认为这种逻辑会把责任归咎于性骚扰的受害者，并会误导民众认为只有弱女子才会受到骚扰<ref name="cbs-quote">{{Cite news|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/news/eric-trump-weighs-in-on-his-fathers-comments-on-the-khan-family/|title=Eric Trump weighs in on father's feud with fallen soldier's parents|last=Shabbad|first=Rebecca|date=2016-08-02|work=CBS News|accessdate=2016-08-02|archive-date=2021-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117081438/https://www.cbsnews.com/news/eric-trump-weighs-in-on-his-fathers-comments-on-the-khan-family/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 批评者包括格雷琴卡尔森，前[[福斯新聞頻道|福克斯新闻]]首席执行官Roger Ailes、 [[梅根·凯利|梅根·凯利]]。<ref name="fox-critics">[https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/donald-and-eric-trump-opine-on-sexual-harassment--and-draw-fire/2016/08/02/9814549e-58c5-11e6-9aee-8075993d73a2_story.html Trump on how women should deal with harassment: It's ‘up to the individual’] {{Wayback|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/donald-and-eric-trump-opine-on-sexual-harassment--and-draw-fire/2016/08/02/9814549e-58c5-11e6-9aee-8075993d73a2_story.html |date=20160802195935 }}, The Washington Post, August 2, 2016.</ref>

== 个人生活 ==
2013年7月4日，埃里克与其女友[[廣播聯賣|银团]]电视新闻节目Inside Edition的副制片人Lara Lea Yunaska订婚。这对情侣举办了一场“水晶点缀般”的庆典；<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.people.com/people/gallery/0,,20871219_30248420,00.html#30248417/|title=Eric Trump & Lara Yunaska's Wedding Album|accessdate=2014-11-10|publisher=People|website=People.com|archive-date=2014-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141111153606/http://www.people.com/people/gallery/0%2C%2C20871219_30248420%2C00.html#30248417/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2014年11月8日他们在佛罗里达[[棕榈滩|棕榈滩]]的[[Mar-a-Lago|Mar-a-Lago]]俱乐部举行了婚礼。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/gossip/eric-trump-marries-lara-yunaska-palm-beach-wedding-article-1.2004472|title=Eric Trump marries Lara Yunaska in Palm Beach wedding|website=NY Daily News|access-date=2016-03-20|archive-date=2016-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160319214522/http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/gossip/eric-trump-marries-lara-yunaska-palm-beach-wedding-article-1.2004472|dead-url=no}}</ref>2017年，長子出生。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Puente|first1=Maria|title=Eric and Lara Trump announce birth of son, POTUS' ninth grandchild|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/2017/09/12/eric-and-lara-trump-announce-birth-son-potus-ninth-grandchild/658130001/|accessdate=2017-09-12|newspaper=USA Today|date=2017-09-12|archive-date=2017-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170912190205/https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/2017/09/12/eric-and-lara-trump-announce-birth-son-potus-ninth-grandchild/658130001/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2019年，長女出生。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Yasharoff|first1=Hannah|title=Eric and Lara Trump welcome second baby, President Trump's 10th grandchild: 'We love you already!'|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/parenting/2019/08/20/president-donald-trump-tenth-grandchild-eric-lara-trump-welcome-second-kid/2059106001/|accessdate=2019-08-20|newspaper=USA Today|date=2019-08-20|archive-date=2020-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201225011417/https://www.usatoday.com/story